\c 15 Azaria mambo waJudha 1 Negore ramakumi maviri na- manomwe raJerobhoamu maâ€‘ mbo waIsiraeri, Azaria mwanakomana waAmazia mambo waJudha wakatanga kubata ushe. 2 Wakanga anamakore ane gumi namatanhatu pakutanga kwake kubata ushe, akabata ushe paJerusaremu makore ana makumi mashanu namaviri; zita ramai vake rakanga riri Jekoria weJerusaremu. 3 Akaita zvakarurama pamberi paJehovha, sezvakaita baba vake Amazia pazvose. 4 Kunyange zvakadaro, matunhu akakwirira haana kubviswa, vanhu vakaramba vachibayira nokupisa zvinonhuwira pamatunhu akakwirira. 5 Jehovha akarova mambo, akava namaperembudzi kusvikira zuva rokufa kwake, akagara ari oga muimba. Jotamu mwanakomana wamambo akava mutariri weimba, akatongawo mhosva dzavanhu venyika. 6 Zvino mamwe mabasa aAzaria, nezvose zvaakaita, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku yamakoronike amadzimambo aJudha? 7 Azaria akavata namadzibaba ake, vakamuviga kuna madzibaba ake muguta raDhavhidhi; Jotamu mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
